1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 2=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,040
What are you doing?

18
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,680
Yu,

19
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,800
she's obviously here to cause trouble.

20
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,440
You don't have to
defend the Zhou family.

21
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:25,200
I have to.
She's slandering the Zhou family.

22
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,200
Enough.

23
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,160
Just stay here.

24
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:28,800
I'll handle it.

25
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,240
You will?

26
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,800
Zhou's Fabrics is cheating people

27
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,800
by selling fakes!

28
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,160
Everyone, come and see!

29
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,040
What's this ruckus?

30
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,280
And who are you?

31
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:40,400
Me?

32
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,720
I represent the Zhou family.

33
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:44,160
Who do you think you are,

34
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:46,560
claiming you speak for the Zhou family?

35
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,040
Though unworthy,

36
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:51,280
I am Li Yunhe,
the Zhou live-in son-in-law.

37
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,840
A live-in son-in-law?

38
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,320
Is the Zhou family
that hard up for talent?

39
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:05,340
(Zhao Ziyao, Princess of Daqian Dynasty
Zhao Yunzhuo, Emperor of Daqian Dynasty)

40
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,680
He's got a decent face,
I'll give him that.

41
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,560
Too bad

42
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:11,240
he's the scumbag who visited
a brothel on his wedding night.

43
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,720
If you ask me,

44
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,600
a guy like that should be castrated

45
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,640
and sent to the palace,

46
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:18,720
then flogged daily with a saltwater whip
and put to work

47
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:19,480
turning a millstone.

48
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,640
That's quite vicious.

49
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,920
Spending all that money every year

50
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,160
on such shoddy goods?

51
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:24,960
I say

52
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,040
we should strip them
of their imperial supplier status,

53
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,200
then charge the Zhou family

54
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,600
with deceiving the throne

55
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,600
and execute the whole clan

56
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,000
to make an example of them.

57
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,480
As a young lady,

58
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:34,480
you're always talking about
blood and killing.

59
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,160
What's wrong with a live-in son-in-law?

60
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,120
Who'd dare marry you?

61
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,360
I can still hold up the family name.

62
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,800
Let me check it.

63
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,280
This Rustling Silk you bought

64
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,160
is not fake.

65
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,280
However,

66
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,320
it's not the top-tier quality
from our shop.

67
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,520
(Is this guy)

68
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,600
(an idiot?)

69
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,320
Sir, what are you saying?

70
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,280
Just hear me out.

71
00:02:59,080 --> 00:02:59,880
My lady...

72
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:00,920
Hold on, don't fret.

73
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,600
Let's see what he has to say first.

74
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,360
Our signature Rustling Silk,

75
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,640
as the name suggests,

76
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,640
when worn,

77
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:08,720
makes a distinctive rustling sound,
hence the name.

78
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:11,200
Its production process
is incredibly complex.

79
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,760
It takes steaming,
boiling, sun-drying, etc.,

80
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:16,200
over 30 steps in total to finish.

81
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,560
We don't even have 30 steps.

82
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,600
Only 15.

83
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:22,160
Is Mr. Li just making this up?

84
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,200
Never mind that for now.

85
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,280
Let's see how he handles this.

86
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,080
Freshly into the family,

87
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,120
and he's already got
the Zhous wrapped around his finger.

88
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,200
Talent like that is rare.

89
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,320
If you ask me,

90
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:33,720
he should be castrated
and sent to the palace.

91
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,400
He'd definitely

92
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,400
be a cunning servant
with a bag of tricks.

93
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,400
Nonsense.

94
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,400
After all that,

95
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,200
do you get it now?

96
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,080
No.

97
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,680
Uh, I mean...

98
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,240
Does all that talk change anything?

99
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,600
Can it change the fact
that you sold fakes?

100
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,920
Look at this, everyone.

101
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,080
This is Zhou's Fabrics'...

102
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,680
Shut it!

103
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,400
Like I just said,

104
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,920
this is not a fake.

105
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,800
But

106
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,800
it's not our shop's

107
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,440
absolute top-tier quality.

108
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,680
What I described earlier

109
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,440
is the imperial tribute grade.

110
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:04,600
For someone like you,

111
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,240
wearing Rustling Silk
made with a simpler process

112
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,640
is more than enough.

113
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,880
What do you mean, "someone like me"?

114
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:11,480
You've talked a big game.

115
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,800
So bring out this tribute-grade

116
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,880
Rustling Silk

117
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,880
you keep boasting about.

118
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,520
I'll buy as much as you have.

119
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:18,200
Hope you keep that promise.

120
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,720
Yu.

121
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,080
Bring out the goods.

122
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:21,640
Huh?

123
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,280
What goods?

124
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,600
We don't have any.

125
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,720
I hereby declare

126
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,120
that starting now,

127
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,400
the tribute-grade Rustling Silk

128
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,600
will officially be added
to the inventory

129
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,360
of Zhou's Fabrics.

130
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,560
Order now while stocks last.

131
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,800
First come, first served.

132
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,920
Over 30 steps in the process?

133
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,560
This has got to be good.

134
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,440
Hey, sir,

135
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:47,680
how much is
this tribute-grade Rustling Silk?

136
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,680
Fine words are cheap.

137
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,680
How can you prove

138
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,560
this so-called imperial tribute

139
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,840
is actually quality stuff?

140
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,800
You may not trust my judgment,

141
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,000
but surely you can't question

142
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,360
the eye of an imperial tribute selector.

143
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,160
Everyone,

144
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,640
before leaving home today,

145
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:04,160
I made a point of discussing this
with Ms. Zhou.

146
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,600
Starting today,

147
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,080
we're launching a presale event

148
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,760
for the tribute-grade

149
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:09,800
Rustling Silk.

150
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,800
Who wants some?

151
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,160
I do!

152
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:12,960
I do!

153
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:19,500
(Zhou's Fabrics)

154
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,840
Excuse me, please make way.

155
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:26,840
Everyone,

156
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,880
inside here

157
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:30,200
is our imperial tribute-grade
Rustling Silk.

158
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,160
The market price is

159
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,760
99.8 taels.

160
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,160
But today, you get a discount.

161
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,360
For 99.8 taels,

162
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:39,000
you don't get just one piece,

163
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,360
or two pieces,

164
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,160
but three pieces.

165
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,560
99.8 taels?

166
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,480
No.

167
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,880
The limited-time special price

168
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:45,920
is just

169
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,680
68.8 taels!

170
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,800
68.8 taels for all this?

171
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,440
Isn't that still a bit pricey?

172
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:57,240
That's a great question, young lady.

173
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,720
68.8 taels

174
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,960
is indeed no small sum

175
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,400
for ordinary folks.

176
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,480
But as citizens of Feng City,

177
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,600
you all matter to me.

178
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,560
I see you as my family.

179
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,960
My goal today

180
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,680
is to bring benefits to you folks.

181
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:13,240
Three pieces of imperial tribute-grade
Rustling Silk.

182
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,640
68.8 taels?

183
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,360
No.

184
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,160
38.8 taels?

185
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,680
Still no.

186
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,640
Today's flash sale price

187
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:22,440
is just

188
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,920
19.8 taels!

189
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,760
19.8 taels?

190
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:26,960
Where's the applause?

191
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,880
And that's not all.

192
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,760
For you folks, I've also secured

193
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,600
a Rustling Silk folding fan

194
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,360
and a Rustling Silk purse.

195
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,160
Miss it today,

196
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,680
and you'll wait till next year.

197
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,600
Limited quantity.

198
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,840
Order now!

199
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:41,360
Yu,

200
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,080
put them on the shelf!

201
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:42,840
Huh?

202
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:44,760
Put out the stock.

203
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,760
All this stock,

204
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,680
and it's the tribute-grade
Rustling Silk!

205
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,160
It costs less than 20 taels?

206
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,560
I'll take it!

207
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,120
Me too!

208
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,480
Right this way.

209
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,400
- I want some too!
- I want some too!

210
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:56,440
- Me too!
- Me too!

211
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,600
Yu,

212
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,960
record the sales, hurry.

213
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,560
Okay.

214
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:01,400
Chunxiang, help out now.

215
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:01,880
Go help.

216
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:02,920
Easy now.

217
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,560
Plenty for everyone.

218
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:15,880
Yunzhuo.

219
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,960
Li Yunhe is actually quite something.

220
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,240
I'm almost tempted to buy some myself.

221
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,440
Exactly.

222
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:24,000
So much tribute-grade Rustling Silk

223
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,280
for less than 20 taels?

224
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,280
What a bargain.

225
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,720
You used to keep pestering me

226
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,960
to remove Rustling Silk
from the imperial tribute list.

227
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,440
So what's this now?

228
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,520
I just felt like buying some.

229
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,040
Yunzhuo,

230
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,560
just stay out of my business.

231
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,120
We're rich!

232
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,320
In a single day, we sold

233
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,920
as much as we usually do in half a year.

234
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,400
Mr. Li,

235
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,600
you're amazing!

236
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,840
It's quite unexpected.

237
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,480
Li Yunhe,

238
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,760
not only can you match verses,

239
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,440
but you're pretty sharp at business too.

240
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,320
If I'd handled this today,

241
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,920
I'm not sure
I'd have done as well as you.

242
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,360
Exactly!

243
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,240
Even that woman
who came to stir up trouble

244
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,720
put in a preorder.

245
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,440
Mr. Li,

246
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,840
your way of handling things
is incredible.

247
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,600
It's nothing.

248
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,160
(Just some livestream sales pitch)

249
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,440
(I heard a million times
before transmigration.)

250
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,200
(Piece of cake.)

251
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,080
(All it takes is talk.)

252
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:18,540
(Marquis House)

253
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,000
My lord, look.

254
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,480
Pretty nice, right?

255
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,440
Wasn't spending that 20 taels worth it?

256
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,520
It's really...

257
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,080
You useless idiot!

258
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:33,120
I sent you to cause trouble
at Zhou's Fabrics.

259
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,600
And what did you achieve?

260
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,920
Not only did you fail,

261
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,040
but you even threw away 20 taels

262
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,000
and brought me back this scrap of paper?

263
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:41,720
My lord,

264
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,400
that's not scrap paper.

265
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,440
It's a presale voucher.

266
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:48,000
With this, you can claim

267
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,040
eight items

268
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,280
made of tribute-grade Rustling Silk.

269
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,240
It's a super good deal.

270
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,120
Guards!

271
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,920
My lord,

272
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,240
Mr. Chen, the top scholar, is here.

273
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,480
Drag her out!

274
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,920
It's not my fault, my lord!

275
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,560
Li Yunhe is to blame!

276
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,720
His words were just too tempting!

277
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:09,400
Li Yunhe.

278
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,760
The Zhous.

279
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,880
They've slipped through my grasp again.

280
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,680
Chen.

281
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,720
Greetings, my lord.

282
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,000
Smoke veils the pond-side willow?

283
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,840
He shows some refinement after all,
my lord.

284
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,440
This is the first line

285
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,000
that had you stumped?

286
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:32,880
Ridiculous.

287
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:35,440
As if I would be stumped.

288
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:38,000
I was just about to have him killed

289
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,680
when, unfortunately,

290
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:42,400
someone from the Zhou family
shielded him.

291
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,640
Smoke veils the pond-side willow.

292
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:48,120
It hides the five elements.

293
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,400
There's no perfect match.

294
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,040
Mr. Chen,

295
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,520
can't you match it either?

296
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:55,680
Hmm?

297
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:00,000
My apologies, I spoke out of turn.

298
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,640
Chen,

299
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,920
Li Yunhe

300
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:05,560
has foiled my plans time and again.

301
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,880
You must think of something for me,

302
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:12,320
so I can finally vent this grudge.

303
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,840
He's merely an illiterate lowlife.

304
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,240
Dealing with him isn't hard.

305
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,880
The tricky part is his status
as the Zhou son-in-law.

306
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,640
After all, the Zhous...

307
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:24,040
So, is there a way

308
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:25,680
to bypass the Zhous

309
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,120
and help me achieve my goal?

310
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,640
I just returned from the capital

311
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,040
and brought back some news about them.

312
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,560
The capital?

313
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,920
About the Zhous?

314
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,520
Is it about the Rustling Silk?

315
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,240
Yes.

316
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,600
Rustling Silk has been stripped

317
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,280
of its imperial tribute status.

318
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:46,280
The official notice
from the court to Feng City

319
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,840
should arrive within the next few days.

320
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:48,880
Is that true?

321
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:49,640
Absolutely.

322
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:50,880
Good!

323
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,480
Excellent.

324
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:55,120
Rustling Silk
loses its imperial tribute status,

325
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:58,560
and Li Yunhe dared
to sell goods under the royal name.

326
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,280
Oh, Li Yunhe,

327
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,920
the happier you sold it previously,

328
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,440
the more miserable your end will be.

329
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,240
Go

330
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,840
spread this news.

331
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,920
I want all of Feng City to know.

332
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,440
Not so fast, my lord.

333
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,480
I suggest we delay

334
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,320
this news traveling from the capital

335
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,320
for a few more days.

336
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,760
You've been pacing for two hours.

337
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,800
Aren't you tired?

338
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,320
I am tired.

339
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,000
Mentally exhausted.

340
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,040
He's just a cast-off son-in-law.

341
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,440
What gives him the right
to go around saying

342
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,720
he represents the Zhou family?

343
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,400
I don't see anything wrong

344
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:42,680
with what Li Yunhe said.

345
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:45,240
It's true that I haven't signed
the divorce papers.

346
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:47,040
That means he's still
part of the Zhou family,

347
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,520
still my husband.

348
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:50,640
It's perfectly fine for him
to represent us.

349
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:51,920
He's nothing

350
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,480
but a broke,
illiterate good-for-nothing.

351
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,840
What does he know about Rustling Silk

352
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,320
or running a shop?

353
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,880
He knows nothing.

354
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,400
The first thing out of his mouth

355
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:02,840
was that the Zhous'
Rustling Silk is just average,

356
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:05,440
and that we have much better ones.

357
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,320
With him pulling a stunt like this,

358
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,720
how is Zhou's Fabrics
supposed to keep doing business?

359
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,120
This sales method of Li Yunhe's...

360
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,080
Maybe

361
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:15,280
we should roll it out

362
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,400
across all our family's stores.

363
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:17,520
What?

364
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,760
All our stores?

365
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:19,400
Yeah.

366
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,480
Have you lost your mind?

367
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,320
That's...

368
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:24,400
That's something
Li Yunhe just came up with on a whim.

369
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,800
You want to launch it in every store?

370
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,280
Ugh.

371
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,680
Oh, Huaijin,

372
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:30,480
you don't understand.

373
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:33,400
Once this sales method takes off,

374
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,200
our family's

375
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,720
annual revenue will jump
by at least 30 percent.

376
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:39,680
We can collect payment
before delivering goods,

377
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,680
completely eliminating

378
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,120
the problem of excess inventory.

379
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,440
Fine, you get it,

380
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,440
but I don't.

381
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:45,920
Do whatever you want.

382
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:46,520
I'm leaving.

383
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,920
You'll understand someday.

384
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:54,360
Li Yunhe's really quite outstanding.

385
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,520
My lord.

386
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:08,320
What's the situation outside?

387
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,520
It's uncanny.

388
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:12,240
Just as Mr. Chen predicted,

389
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,160
Li Yunhe's sales tactic

390
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,400
has been adopted

391
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,720
by all the Zhou family's stores.

392
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,760
My lord,

393
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:21,840
it's time to let the wind
from the capital blow in.

394
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:54,380
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

395
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:57,740
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

396
00:13:58,260 --> 00:14:00,980
♪Who took the March rain♪

397
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:04,580
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

398
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:07,740
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

399
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:11,100
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

400
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:17,900
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

401
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:21,380
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

402
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:24,460
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

403
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:26,900
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

404
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:31,100
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

405
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:34,460
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

406
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:37,740
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

407
00:14:38,260 --> 00:14:41,180
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

408
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:47,860
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

409
00:15:14,140 --> 00:15:17,660
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

410
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:21,060
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

411
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:24,380
♪Who took the March rain♪

412
00:15:24,580 --> 00:15:27,900
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

413
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:31,180
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

414
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:34,980
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

415
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:38,300
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

416
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:41,260
♪As seasons change♪

417
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:44,900
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

418
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:47,740
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

419
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:50,380
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

420
00:15:50,380 --> 00:15:54,460
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

421
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:57,780
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

422
00:15:57,780 --> 00:16:01,500
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

423
00:16:01,900 --> 00:16:05,020
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

424
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:07,900
♪Only for you♪

425
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:11,500
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

426
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:14,380
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

427
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:17,060
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

428
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:21,140
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

429
00:16:21,140 --> 00:16:24,460
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

430
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:27,860
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

431
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:34,380
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

432
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:39,580
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

433
00:16:40,860 --> 00:16:45,380
♪Your wedding gown♪
